data.message: If we could connect to one billion people, we would invite them to join our Extraordinary Breath Campaign, set to launch on Wednesday, October 10, 2012, on Indiegogo.com, set to launch on Wednesday, October 10th, 2012. The goal, with this crowd-funding Extraordinary Breath Campaign, is to enhance the health and wellbeing of everyone through conscious, intentional, deep breathing, using cutting edge technology merged with ancient wisdom for greater health and happiness, creating Apps, eBooks and World Events.  Please check it out pre-launch at http://www.ExtraordinaryBreath.com!
